              readings transmitted in the witnesses are problematic. \msM, a MS not collated for
              this chapter, gives a confusing reading: Łsa<UNCL>murdhni</UNCL>dam$. I doubt
              if \Ed's Łsamṛddhidam$ (`yielding success') is the correct reading.
